## 사건 정보

**사건명**: The People of the State of New York v. Joseph C. Sheehan
**판결일**: 1953-09-28
**법원**: Appellate Division of the Supreme Court of the State of New York
**관할**: New York, NY

## 인용

- 282 A.D. 843

## 판결문 요약


Defendant appeals from an order denying his motion in the nature of coram nobis to vacate a judgment convicting him of murder in the second degree, entered upon his plea of guilty. Order affirmed. No opinion. Adel, Acting P. J., Wenzel, MaeCrate, Schmidt and Beldock, JJ., concur.
